author: domingothegamer
description: Reaction roles that the bot receives and does actions accordingly.
end_user_data_statement:
This cog stores User ID's for the purposes of re-assigning roles when the user re-joins a server.
User ID's may be stored in the bots log information.
install_msg: The command group is `[p]reactcmds`. Remember that role names are case sensitive.
name: ReactCmds
short: Reacts via Emoji and does commands.
